{"tid":3884,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"東九龍踢波group招人","createTime":"2016-11-26T10:13:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-05T03:49:42.000Z","uid":1742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"19e670db0403162e86e03681b3e1426187833a22","tid":3884,"uid":1742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T10:13:13.000Z","msg":"是咁的 之前同班巴打組左個足球group<br />\n<br />\n暫時有20人 依家想再招新血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n主要係黃大仙、觀塘踢<br />\n<br />\n通常平日夜晚或六日踢<br />\n<br />\n我地志在出汗 唔會要求好勁<br />\n<br />\n實力真係中下級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n識傳下波、走下位<br />\n<br />\n最重要有球品、斯文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋每次有bk 場後 <br />\n<br />\n盡快上水覆group ( 我做搞手都要覆人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n技術高低不重要<br />\n<br />\n最重要係有心踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有意就pm我你地電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60ae0a5bae3f8fa3c00df6b148a4532dd1a81be0","tid":3884,"uid":1707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:43:13.000Z","msg":"好似冇得pm住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f02860ae764f659fd6410dc8f23a7cd578474617","tid":3884,"uid":23878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:28:35.000Z","msg":"我想踢波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小學後未踢高波"},{"pid":"65040c7d0249b42a780d7eaf893a649b44c02b2c","tid":3884,"uid":6658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T06:53:13.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"773650751fd32a730faabfecd6c5fb88638f99c4","tid":3884,"uid":11081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T07:00:31.000Z","msg":"無pm點算"},{"pid":"5f10fb35bb6420e84b4ddc419afb95ae03c8868f","tid":3884,"uid":15262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":